to track untracked files :-
1.click on the + sign, right next to file.
2.now write in the message box : First commit after re-enabling track.
3.then click sync message.

to update details in file :-
1. 1st steps is same as the untracked files steps.
2. write updated file name in message box.
e.g. updated index.html,
3. same as the 3rd steps as above.